<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.2">
<l>tāyar maṉaṅkaḷ taṭippat tayirneyyuṇ</l>
<l>ṭēyem pirākka ḷirunilat teṅkaḷtam</l>
<l>āya raḻaka vaṭika ḷaravinta</l>
<l>vāyava ṉēkoṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">mālvaṇṇa ṉēkoṭṭāy cappāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our devious mighty one, eating curds and ghee</l>
<l>So the ladies’ hearts harden,</l>
<l>Our beauty of the herders on the vast earth, god,</l>
<l>The one of lotus lips, clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">dark-hued one, clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
